            "title": "笑到最後｜哈！哈！哈！（高明）",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Yahoo連載嘅笑到最後終於最後一篇，感謝Yahoo財經一直將所有標題同內文直出，哈哈哈哈哈哈！\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"701\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/BgLal8j6P9pvDaXNaSJWCQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcwMQ--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/c5d3b270-2a58-11f1-9e7f-4936b03b3b00\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Yahoo連載嘅笑到最後終於最後一篇，感謝Yahoo財經一直將所有標題同內文直出，哈哈哈哈哈哈！</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">最後一篇，直接嚟啦！</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link rapid-with-clickid etailiffa-link athena-button\" data-i13n=\"sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Yahoo;elmt:other;pdid:\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"1\",\"yLinkElement\":\"affiliate_link\",\"yAffiliateService\":\"other\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"shop-now\",\"ySellerName\":\"Yahoo\",\"yLinkText\":\"下載Yahoo財經APP\",\"yHasCommerce\":true}' data-ylk=\"slk:下載Yahoo財經APP;sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Yahoo;elmt:other;pdid:;itc:0\" href=\"https://mobile.yahoo.com/finance?pid=editorial&amp;c=HK_Acquisition_YMktg_Evergreen_article_&amp;af_sub1=Acquisition&amp;af_sub2=HK_YMktg&amp;af_sub4=1058&amp;af_sub5=article__Banner_\">下載Yahoo財經APP</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>美股外幣即時報價 多國新聞任睇</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">一、炫富係市場學marketing</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">網上流行貼倉炫富，今日有片都冇真相嘅年代，你唔係信呀？</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">好多網上KOL自稱幾多幾多億都係市場學，曾有90後財演自稱一年賺一千萬，因一份8000月薪嘅工畀人炒咗，同社長反面發晒脾氣，反差太大。自此高明唔再信呢啲marketing。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">更重要係，佢有錢，上網曬命，會唔會分一半出嚟，見者有份？想乞likes但唔想跌？慳啲啦。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2d674eb3-9bb8-4a10-b512-09227807ed04-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">二、跑贏大市迷思</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">基金有條數，將自己個基金同指數比較，每年要跑贏被動指數，證明嗰兩成表現費畀得值。喺呢個角度作出比較有合理性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但將呢條無謂嘅線拉咗去個人股市創業者度，真係九唔搭八，個人持股一唔使同人交代，二唔使sell客。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">事實上，如果個人股市創業者唔係住公屋、食老豆老母，好難將每分每毫全部放晒去股票戶口到，食住行玩儲備點都住一定比例，股票一般只佔身家一部份。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">既然資產有一定比例都係非股票資產，跑唔跑贏指數已無意思。明明係自由之身，點解要裝隻蘿蔔吊喺自己面前跑做驢仔呢？</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">三、TACO照蠢鏡</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">任何人今日仲用TACO一字作投資論點，嗰個KOL就係弱智。TACO重點在於A字嘅Always每次。當撈侵有冇縮？有；有冇次次縮？冇。簡單語理邏輯都唔通，廣東話使用者本有更精準用語：開天殺價落地還錢，唔用，走去用創作弱智字，遠東投資KOL爭相舔啜，見證呢班投資KOL嘅墮落。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Yahoo連載嘅笑到最後終於最後一篇，感謝Yahoo財經一直將所有標題同內文直出，哈哈哈哈哈哈！</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高明</p></div>",
